Description: Fast plotting functions for flow cytometry data visualization.
             C-based conversion of large scatterplot data to rasters plus other 
             operations such as data blurring or data alpha blending. This package
             incorporates code and concepts from the scattermore package 
             (https://github.com/exaexa/scattermore) for fast scatterplot rendering.
             Version 1.1 adds optimized functions using raw uint8_t arrays for 
             improved performance.
             1.111 remove the dependency on the 'flowWorkspace' package.
             1.112 added reduced plotting margins to the 'plot' function. 
             1.113 update f.parseChannels for exactly match "\\b" "V660-A"/"UV660-A"
             1.114 update f.parseChannels overhall for better channel matching
             1.115 update f.parseChannels for better channel matching "\\b"
             1.116 supress warnings in f.parseChannels
             1.117 plotting gates and trans error fixed
             1.118 flowplot function added minimum cell number for density estimation
             1.119 Fixed flowplot function bug when there is no cell
             1.120 add gate color argument
             1.121 log fsc ssc labels; shorter label options
             1.122 remove unrelavant autoflow_colors variable
             1.123 fix plotting background pop bug
             1.124 add subtitle(right side) and margin color to the plot function
             1.125 highlight tweaks
             1.126 add highlight.alpha
             1.127 highligh bug fix          
             1.128 remove the annoying print message
             1.130 fix class check bug
             1.131 fix plot function bug when there is only 1 cell
